&lt;h1 id="shraddha-on-guru">Shraddha On Guru&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#shraddha-on-guru" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="guru-purnima-2021">Guru Purnima 2021&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#guru-purnima-2021" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Darkness was prevalent all over &lt;br>
Because it was dark everywhere outside &lt;br>
There was no light physical.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Darkness was prevalent all over &lt;br>
Because it was dark in society. &lt;br>
People were deluded, &lt;br>
They were not able to identify &lt;br>
what is right or wrong for them. &lt;br>
They are not able to choose &lt;br>
between right and wrong for others.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Gunasagar Nirguna Paramesha - गुणसागर निर्गुण परमेशा</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/gunasagar-nirguna/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/gunasagar-nirguna/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/Sri-Ramakrishna.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
