&lt;h1 id="गर-सततरम">गुरु स्तोत्रम्&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%97%e0%a4%b0-%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%a4%e0%a4%a4%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%ae" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="guru-stotram">Guru Stotram&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#guru-stotram" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/57-GuruStotram057-GuruStotram.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>गुरुर्ब्रह्मा गुरुर्विष्णुर्गुरुर्देवो महेश्वरः । &lt;br>
गुरुरेव परं ब्रह्म तस्मै श्रीगुरवे नमः ॥१॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>अज्ञानतिमिरान्धस्य ज्ञानाञ्जनशालाकया । &lt;br>
चक्षुरुन्मीलितं येन तस्मै श्रीगुरवे नमः ॥२॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Gurvashtaka - गुर्वष्टकम्</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/gurvashtaka/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/gurvashtaka/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/Sri-Ramakrishna.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="गरवषटकम">गुर्वष्टकम्&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%97%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%b5%e0%a4%b7%e0%a4%9f%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%ae" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="gurvashtaka">Gurvashtaka&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#gurvashtaka" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/013-GuruvAshtakam.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>शरीरं सुरुपं तथा वा कलत्रं यशश्चारू चित्रं धनं मेरुतुल्यम् । &lt;br>
मनश्चेन्न लग्नं गुरोरंघ्रिपद्मे ततः किं ततः किं ततः किं ततः किम् ।।१।।&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Relevance Of Guru</title><link>https://localhost:1313/wiaposts/relevance-of-guru/</link><pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/wiaposts/relevance-of-guru/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/wiapost/5115-Relevance-Of-Guru.jpg" alt="Relevance Of Guru">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="relevance-of-guru">Relevance Of Guru&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#relevance-of-guru" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Without Questions in life what is the need for a Guru? &lt;br>
If my questions are well defined then do I need a Guru? &lt;br>
Guru helps in defining questions well &lt;br>
or answering whatever you ask? &lt;br>
Does he empower you by giving more information &lt;br>
or make you restless by holding half answer?&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Who Is Guru</title><link>https://localhost:1313/wiaposts/who-is-guru/</link><pubDate>Tue, 30 Aug 2016 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/wiaposts/who-is-guru/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/wiapost/5029-Who-Is-Guru.jpg" alt="Who Is Guru">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="who-is-guru">Who Is Guru&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#who-is-guru" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>We all know the Samskrut definition of Guru &lt;br>
The remover of darkness. &lt;br>
But whose darkness? &lt;br>
How does he remove? &lt;br>
What is this darkness about? &lt;br>
What is the meaning of remove?&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>